{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "赵无忌离开唐家堡后决定去找司空晓风共商反攻大计。他途经银杏镇，在一家面店被伙计以抄手试探是否为唐家堡同路人。冲突中赵无忌击杀伙计及埋伏的唐家堡手下八人，当众宣告自己的身份与大风堂必将收复失土的决心。之后他来到另一被唐家堡接管的小镇，遇面摊老板（实为暗杀组织负责人胡贩）讲述唐家堡暴行及张老头女儿被逼婚的事。赵无忌决定出手相助，于初更时来到张宅。张老头声称是大风堂忠臣，赵无忌表明身份欲带他们逃离。不料张老头实为暗杀组织负责人张大嘴，其\"女儿\"为其妻李无绝，三人合谋设局诱捕赵无忌。赵无忌被制住后，胡贩现身点其穴道，三人计划把他交给唐家堡换取重赏。赵无忌声称是唐傲放他出来的，但三人不信，强行将他带走。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官请里面坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官想吃点什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "随便。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官是要大随便，还是小随便？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "什么是大随便，什么是小随便？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "大随便嘛，就给你来一大碗卤面，小随便嘛，就给你一碗小磨麻油酸辣抄手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你们这里也卖抄手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是呀！昨天才开始的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "昨天才开始？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是呀，我们店本来没有卖的。昨天开始，来了很多人都要吃抄手，我们不得不卖了。不过，这东西蛮好吃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "昨天临时才卖，你们会它吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不会呀，是有人来兜卖的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官你也知道呀？唐家堡的人生意经好快啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官到底要不要来一碗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "好吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好吃吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "唔，还不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你喜欢吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我很喜欢。你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "我觉得很好吃，不过我不喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "因为我不习惯吃辣的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不习惯？不习惯也得习惯才成呀？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你为什么要偷袭我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为你不是唐家堡的人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我怎么知道？谁都可以看出来。唐家堡的人吃抄手，哪会像你这样慢吞吞的吃法？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "我就算不是唐家堡的人，你也用不着杀我呀？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "用得着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为我们才刚接管这个银杏镇。这里原本是大风堂的势力范围，我们绝不让任何一个残余份子留在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你们把镇上的人都杀了吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "只要肯归顺的，就没杀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "哼！好个唐家堡，是唐傲叫你们这样做的吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐傲？唐傲是不会叫我们这样做的，他太仁慈了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "那是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "当然是比唐傲更有权力的人么，不然，我们怎么敢公然的叫唐傲这个字？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "是老祖宗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你也知道老祖宗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "何止知道，还见过。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "哦？那你是唐家堡的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "不，我是大风堂的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "你能施偷袭，我当然也能。而且我生平是第一次偷袭人家。因为我太看你不顺眼了。唐傲的名字，也是你可以随便乱叫的吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是唐家堡的人吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢逃走？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是大风堂的赵无忌。大风堂是不能被人家欺侮的！唐家堡的下场就有如此屋！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们放心好了，我们大风堂一定会收复这块失土的，你们好自为之吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "你以前卖的牛肉面是不辣的，对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官以前来吃过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "没有，我第一次来到这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "哦？客官的嘴好厉害，一吃就知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "你的摊子这么陈旧，这表示你的生意一定做了很久，可是这辣味嘛，却一点也不香，假如用这样的口味来招揽客人，我想不到三个月就要收摊了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官说得一点也不错。可是，唉——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "你有什么难言之隐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "也不是什么难言之隐，你既然是外地来，我就跟你说吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是这样的，以前这镇是大风堂的势力范围，我们按时缴纳费用，一切都很正常，生意也很兴隆。但是在几天前，大风堂被唐家堡打跑了，这里变成由唐家堡来接管。这几天，我们这里根本就什么生意也没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你看到街头上的房子吗？他们有的公然反抗唐家堡，所以房子被打破，人也被捉了。有的则表面听从唐家堡的话，但暗地里却偷偷溜跑了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "唐家堡的人这么凶恶吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "还有更凶的呢！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "哦？是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "张老头怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "怎么办？他能怎么办？唉——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "明天一早，那缪博勇就要来迎娶啦！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "他们怎么不学别人一走了之？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "走，怎么走呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "两只脚在人的身上，走还不简单？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "八个恶汉把你家前后门看守着，你怎么走？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "其实，大风堂的势力已经没落，张老头把女儿嫁给这位新贵，不是挺好的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "客官的话是不错呀，只是，人各有志呀，有些人是忠于大风堂的，脾气又倔，劝不听的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "看门男子",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你找谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "这里的主人呀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "看门男子",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你找他干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "text": "我是来道贺的，听说他明天要嫁女儿，我是他的远房亲戚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mian_dian_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "看门男子",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "进去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你..",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "我找张老爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "张老爷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "是呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我姓张，可是不是老爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你有个女儿明天要出嫁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "那我是找你的，因为有人叫你张老头，所以我..",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我五十几岁了，大概是练武的关系，看起来比较年轻。请进来说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "怎么一个人也没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "都走光了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "怕死嘛！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "外面的人让他们走吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你为什么不化装成佣人的样子走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我能吗？我这么胖，谁都认得出来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你就这样看着你女儿嫁出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我有什么办法？打又打不过人家。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "没打过，你怎么知道打不过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "用得着打吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "用得着。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "因为我刚才进来的时候，只看到两个人守在外面，看他们的样子，武功不怎么样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "我是赵无忌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "怎么，不像吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不是，我是太高兴了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你们顺便收拾一下行李，我们马上走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "叫赵公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "赵公子。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的武功好好啊！我要跟你一起走。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你中计了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "你们是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们？我们当然是来捉你的人喔。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "唐家堡的人，都是用这种不要脸的方法来捉人的吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "那可不一定，对你嘛，还有比这更好的方法吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "是唐傲派你们来捉我的吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我不知道，你问我老公好了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "你老公？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "就是我呀！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "我知道了，你是张大嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，我就是张大嘴。她就是李无绝。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "那个卖面的老头就是胡贩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "完全说对了。只可惜你现在才想到，已经来不及了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "嘻嘻。你瞎了。不是唐家堡出钱要我们对付你的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，是我们想替自己找点财路，主动捉你，好向唐家堡要钱的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐家堡目前正在密锣紧鼓的对付大风堂，你是大风堂的主要角色，捉了你，岂不是大功一件？你想唐家堡会给我们多少钱？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "都怪你自己啦，谁要你在银杏镇上呈英雄，大声说出你自己的身份？要不然，我们也不会赶来这里，预作安排了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不过，也只有你这么蠢的人，才会被我们骗到。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "怎么啦？你瞧不起我们的手段吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "怎么会？任何能捉到对手的手段，都是最好的手段。只不过..",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "只不过什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "只不过你们这次是白费心机啦。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "白费心机？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "因为你们一个钱也拿不到。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "哦？当然是一个钱也拿不到，因为我们会拿到很多个钱。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "不，你们什么也拿不到。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "为什么？难道你现在能逃得了吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "我不必逃。你们把我捉去唐家堡好了。我保证你们除了白费气力、白费精神、白费粮食填我的肚子之外，什么也得不到。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们会相信你的话吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "信不信在你们，到时候别怪我没有先通知你们。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你有什么理由让我们相信你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "text": "我刚从唐家堡出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_wu_jue",
      "speaker_name": "李无绝",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "真的？你怎么出得来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不，应该问你是怎么进得了唐家堡的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_hu_fan",
      "text": "我怎么进去，其实一点也不重要，对你们而言，我怎么出来才是最重要的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好，你说你怎么出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "是唐傲放我出来的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "你们如今又要把我捉回去，岂不是白费心机？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你这种故事，想编来骗我们？哈哈...真是笑死人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "是吗？你怎么还不死？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "张大嘴",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "死的是你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_zui",
      "text": "假如你们不相信我的话，死的不会是我，因为你们需要我活着。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们不要浪费时间在耍嘴皮子啦，我们绝不会相信你的话，你也少讲话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fan",
      "speaker_name": "胡贩",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你现在除了两条腿可以走动以外，什么力气都运不起来。走，跟着我们走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 732
    }
  ],
